@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# 先在浏览器登录 localhost:3000，然后把已登录请求里的 Cookie 粘贴到这里。
# 获取方式：Chrome DevTools -> Network -> 任意 /api 请求 -> Request Headers -> Cookie。
@cookie = paste_your_logged_in_cookie_here

# 改成你本机要测试的 MP3 文件路径。
@audioFile = /Users/joey/Downloads/30s.mp3
@audioFilename = 30s.mp3
@audioMimeType = audio/mpeg
@audioDurationMs = 30000

# 可选：如果你想直接复测某个已有项目，把项目 id 粘贴到这里。
@projectId = paste_existing_project_id_here

### 0. 查看歌词视频项目列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 1. 上传 MP3
# @name uploadAudio
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/storage/upload-audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----lyricVideoBoundary

------lyricVideoBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="{{audioFilename}}"
Content-Type: {{audioMimeType}}

< {{audioFile}}
------lyricVideoBoundary--

### 2. 用上传结果创建歌词视频项目
# @name createProject
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "title": "REST Client Test - {{audioFilename}}",
  "audioUrl": "{{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.url}}",
  "audioStorageKey": "{{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.key}}",
  "originalAudioUrl": "{{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.url}}",
  "originalAudioStorageKey": "{{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.key}}",
  "audioFilename": "{{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.filename}}",
  "audioDurationMs": {{audioDurationMs}},
  "audioMimeType": "{{audioMimeType}}",
  "audioSizeBytes": {{uploadAudio.response.body.$.data.size}},
  "trimStartMs": 0,
  "trimEndMs": {{audioDurationMs}}
}

### 3. 跑 ASR + 本机 Librosa 分析
# @name runAsr
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/asr
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 3b. 对已有项目重新跑 ASR + Librosa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{projectId}}/asr
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 4. 查看刚创建的项目详情
# @name getCreatedProject
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 4b. 查看已有项目详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{projectId}}
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 5. 根据 ASR 结果整理歌词行
# @name normalizeLyrics
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/lyrics/normalize
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 6. 生成 Story Prompt
# @name generateStory
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/story
Cookie: {{cookie}}

### 7. 使用歌词 + 音频分析生成分镜
# @name generateStoryboard
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/storyboard
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{}

### 8. 创建分镜并排队生成缺失的场景图片
# @name generateVisuals
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/visuals
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{cookie}}

{
  "regenerateStoryboard": false,
  "regenerateImages": false
}

### 9. 轮询场景图片生成状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lyric-videos/{{createProject.response.body.$.data.id}}/images
Cookie: {{cookie}}
